    "\n",
    "## Why Multifractality Matters\n",
    "\n",
    "### Beyond Simple Fractals\n",
    "\n",
    "**Simple Fractal (Monofractal)**:\n",
    "- Single scaling exponent (e.g., Brownian motion with H=0.5)\n",
    "- Uniform local behavior\n",
    "- Limited complexity\n",
    "\n",
    "**Multifractal**:\n",
    "- *Multiple* scaling exponents\n",
    "- Heterogeneous local dynamics\n",
    "- Rich temporal structure\n",
    "\n",
    "### Biological Relevance\n",
    "\n",
    "Brain activity exhibits **multifractal scaling**:\n",
    "1. **EEG/MEG**: Multifractal spectra across frequencies\n",
    "2. **fMRI BOLD**: Multifractal temporal organization\n",
    "3. **Spike trains**: Intermittent bursting creates multiscale structure\n",
    "4. **Heart rate variability**: Multifractal = healthy dynamics\n",
    "\n",
    "### Testing NeuroFMx\n",
    "\n",
    "**Key Questions**:\n",
    "- Do NeuroFMx activations exhibit multifractal scaling?\n",
