    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Part 2: Multifractal DFA (MF-DFA)\n",
    "\n",
    "Compute fluctuation functions **F_q(s)** for different moments q.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Method**:\n",
    "1. Integrate signal: Y(i) = Σ[x(k) - <x>]\n",
    "2. Divide into segments of size s\n",
    "3. Detrend each segment (polynomial fit)\n",
    "4. Compute fluctuation: F²(s,ν) = (1/s) Σ[Y(i) - Y_fit(i)]²\n",
    "5. Average over segments: F_q(s) = [<F²(s,ν)^(q/2)>]^(1/q)\n",
    "6. Extract scaling: F_q(s) ~ s^h(q)\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
