    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Part 3: Generalized Hurst Exponents\n",
    "\n",
    "Extract h(q) from scaling: **F_q(s) ~ s^h(q)**\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Monofractal**: h(q) = constant (single H)\n",
    "- **Multifractal**: h(q) varies with q\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
